


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_74878570:


    ve "我以爲我們在小行星帶那要完蛋了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_24bc07c0:


    c "是啊，我們真是千鈞一髮。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_1c56d47e:


    ve "我們現在要去空間站嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_6a5bc48a:


    c "是的，修點東西，也許還去酒吧喝一杯，喫頓像樣的飯。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_a5a0735c:


    ve "聽起來不錯，但會像龍神主星一樣擁擠嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_5c80991f:


    c "可能不會，但空間站地方小多了，所以你可能有跟在龍神上一模一樣的感覺。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_3122994f:


    c "我會陪着你。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_2b6bbb2e:


    c "你要願意，可以待在船上。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_8c8eb389:


    ve "我們現在要去一個行星嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_b623e111:


    c "是的，我們得爲瑞爾弄個樣本。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_975ebe80:


    ve "會很危險嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_1954158b:


    c "很可能，森厄星實在不像是好客的星球。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_29c05164:


    ve "我覺得只要待在船上應該就沒事..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_e413a211:


    c "我會確保你平安無事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_6a6f7432:


    c "就待在船上等我們回來吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_c9685dd2:


    c "說實話，把你拖着到處跑這些地方，我心裡過意不去。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_61c841ca:


    c "從那種寧靜的鄉村生活猛地被扔進這一切，一定很難受吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_b4495192:


    ve "別擔心，這是好事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_4a088bcb:


    ve "到現在還挺刺激的，我覺得我都開始喜歡上了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_5ada39d9:


    c "好吧，肯定還有更多事等着，所以你最好做好心理準備。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_ff0fe41b:


    ve "哈哈，我會的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_44e15297:


    ve "喂，[p_name]？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_0340c4cf:


    c "你要不叫我[p_name_short]也行，大家都這麼叫。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_695cb037:


    ve "好啊，[p_name_short]，在\"至高權域\"這種人多的地方長大是什麼感覺？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_d069622a:


    c "我大半童年都在託洛維星度過，那可不是什麼繁華大都市。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_908c4641:


    ve "你也是在農場長大的？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_4bd791d1:


    c "那倒不是，不過我父母的莊園裡有農場。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_616ba9d6:


    ve "莊園？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_70f5464c:


    ve "所以你父母很有錢？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_6088e8c2:


    c "他們肯定不這麼想，但沒錯，確實有錢。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_60006140:


    c "我覺得除了權力地位，錢就是他們第二看重的東西。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_c1cdf119:


    ve "你父母肯定是愛你的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_2862a3a3:


    c "要真愛我，那他們他媽的可隱藏的真好。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_a6730577:


    ve "呃..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_9f85b645:


    c "是啊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_77ee13d4:


    c "託洛維星的童年不錯，但被送去軍校這事我其實挺慶幸。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_379a4f03:


    c "先不說我了，拉南星生活怎麼樣？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_2b3f063e:


    ve "真沒什麼好說的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_fc736048:


    ve "反正你都見過那地方了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_1064609f:


    c "有人會說那兒古色古香。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_fe66d8bb:


    ve "明白。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_b4f09119:


    ve "老實說滿地泥濘又陰鬱。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_9552f2f6:


    c "你家人呢？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_9aba239b:


    ve "我的...{w}我..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_75f08c2e:


    ve "抱歉[p_name_short]，提這個我還是難受。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_a82d994e:


    c "不想說沒事的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_7fc58ff4:


    ve "我知道...{w}只是..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_6e8b954a:


    ve "每次想起他們，就看見那羣女人抓走他們的場景。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_7e0c3f14:


    ve "我當時怕得要命。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_a74f8a84:


    "薇絲開始哭起來，我就抱着她直到她哭完。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_72685311:


    "等她平靜下來後，這姑娘含着淚道別，想休息一會兒。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_e561d5c9:


    c "抱歉，我不該問的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_e81b45e9:


    ve "沒關係。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_5e323a52:


    "儘管嘴脣在發抖，薇絲還是強作鎮定，但告訴我她想休息會兒。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_b2bc5d37:


    c "嘛，得走了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_vess_talk_fc2db521:


    ve "回頭見。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_talk_32aef856:


    l "嘿[p_name_short]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_talk_85f6289a:


    c "喲，你心情不錯啊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_talk_2d454013:


    l "是啊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_723bcd99:


    l "當初請娜迪亞阿姨跟我們一起走真是明智。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_13134dc9:


    l "當初請娜迪亞跟我們一起走真是明智。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_4df6eb38:


    c "你真這麼想？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_245a5013:


    l "沒錯，你說得對，她確實能幫上忙。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_36c6f2c7:


    l "而且船上有家人感覺真好。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_cbc8cbf4:


    l "而且船上有老朋友感覺真好。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_66ea5c78:


    l "我跟艾文已經連續聊了好幾個鐘頭，太多話要說了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_a4a22269:


    c "而且娜迪亞阿姨看起來根本不恨我們。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_1ae96028:


    c "而且娜迪亞看起來根本不恨我們。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_4ec25b7f:


    l "是的，正好相反。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_202b1a08:


    l "不過她當年走之後就再沒聯繫或來看過我們，是有點奇怪。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_9fbc9199:


    l "但每次我提起父母親，她眼裡就會露出那種眼神。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_d19b841d:


    l "他們之間絕對發生過什麼糟糕透頂的事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_09bd094f:


    c "嗯，我覺得你說得對。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_c9d6eb72:


    c "也許她終究會告訴我們的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_9cf6650b:


    l "但每次我提起過去的事，她眼裡就會露出那種神情。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_0bfd953e:


    l "我敢肯定發生過很糟糕的事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_1fbfcabc:


    c "你或許是對的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_f0176976:


    c "可能她終究會告訴你的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_43ed8f16:


    l "也許吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_4075c0fd:


    l "但眼下我很高興她和我們在一起。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_34f0a009:


    c "你最近還好嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_af7d25b7:


    l "好多了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_93609a59:


    l "不過有時還是覺得心裡空蕩蕩的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_36af312c:


    c "因爲伊娃？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_bc5c265b:


    l "是的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_2a0f2654:


    l "我有時徹夜難眠，回想在拉南星發生的事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_e60907b1:


    l "也許我本可以做些不一樣的抉擇..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_4d666821:


    l "我本可以跟那個揮劍的賤人拼命的！"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_576a2598:


    c "那等於自殺，看看基特的下場。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_76149a5a:


    l "我知道，只是覺得自己好無力。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_ed635fdc:


    l "我們會把她救回來的，對吧？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_20c70dc1:


    c "計劃是這樣的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_fc238aec:


    c "還在生我氣嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_e52b5a00:


    l "不，我覺得沒..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_25850352:


    c "你覺得..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_0920577c:


    l "你知道，這種感覺很難熬。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_d44db7e3:


    l "你一直都很努力不按規矩辦事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_5e3e4c9e:


    l "想到什麼就做什麼..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_cc338f6a:


    l "而我就不是那樣的人。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_395b152e:


    l "選擇那樣叛逃，就把很多選項都堵死了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_b8cb438f:


    c "什麼選項？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_d2a27ada:


    l "比如說，讓\"至高權域\"處理這事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_8935c428:


    c "\"至高權域\"根本不在乎幾個新兵，他們的舉動已經很清楚了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_8fa1767b:


    l "我想你是對的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_1da3908a:


    l "可能你對這些事看得比我清楚，也可能我只是太謹慎了..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_73601177:


    c "也許你是這樣。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_d94c9ee7:


    l "我只是不想也失去你。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_07f3f33e:


    c "做什麼事一頭衝進去也不總是好辦法。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_13db9fab:


    c "所以，拜託，當我下次又要幹蠢事時，告訴我你的顧慮。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_0f03d9cb:


    l "我會的，我也不想失去你。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_e6e09ffa:


    c "艾文告訴我你想來森厄星參與獵捕行動。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_baf50f7f:


    l "是的，我想一起去。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_194c3712:


    l "爲什麼這麼問？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_6ad63f4b:


    c "沒什麼，就是很高興你能來。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_016fdac4:


    l "趁這機會，順便看看風景也好。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_306795e3:


    c "我懂你的意思。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_38ac9a4d:


    l "順便說一句，我以爲你要去睡了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_ed9ad17b:


    c "我是想睡的，但就是睡不着。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_3937287d:


    l "我也很難入睡，飛船的噪音對我來說還很陌生。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_5527f547:


    c "我希望你會喜歡上\"私生子\"號。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_1837ad0e:


    l "很貼切的名字啊，她真的很醜。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_665ae7c6:


    c "我敢肯定侮辱你正乘坐着的飛船會帶來黴運。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_f4a13f0a:


    l "幸好我們不迷信。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_c1bfa14d:


    c "既然你這麼說..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_8dfb4bb9:


    l "總之，我要試着休息會兒，如果船不因怨恨在這期間弄死我的話。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_0a143884:


    c "我會從艦橋監控你的生命信號。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_7654248f:


    l "哈哈，你就那麼做吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_dabbe7b3:


    c "晚安，莉莉。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_bd95dbf0:


    l "晚安，[p_name_short]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_85961719:


    c "我覺得這不是個好主意。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_d5b6fb6c:


    l "我還是不明白你怎麼就覺得自己是頭兒了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_cf148e54:


    l "我非去不可，不管你願不願意。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_d8c7d011:


    c "哼，我就是不願意。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_lilly_dialogue_2ac032ba:


    l "我敢肯定這整個\"[p_name_short]艦長\"的把戲是你自己的一場大權力狂歡，但滾你的吧，我才不在乎！"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_05567bce:


    j "需要什麼嗎，主人？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_b1da6069:


    c "嗯，或許..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_4d08955a:


    c "你做好船體系統的清單了嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_032f4ce3:


    j "是的，我們剛從迅狐星起飛就完成了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_ad096221:


    c "好，那你知道這艘船有VR虛擬現實接口嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_18ab71e1:


    j "這破船是舊了點，但前主人確實裝了一個，沒錯。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_ad046f96:


    j "它在下層機組成員宿舍的單獨房間裡。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_a423fe8e:


    c "塞婭在時沒提過它。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_fdebc71f:


    j "大概覺得它沒那麼要緊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_821d1ce0:


    j "那是個過時的接口，跟市面上現在的完全沒法比。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_b6bf532a:


    c "但它能用。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_669b8bb5:


    j "是的，確實。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_cabc7051:


    j "主人，爲什麼突然對虛擬現實感興趣了？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_e19ee396:


    j "我還以爲說到享樂，你總是更喜歡肢體互動呢？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_53be5100:


    c "那些 VR 接口不光是用於色情模擬的，你知道嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_af71558a:


    j "當然知道，主人，但現在 90%% 的模擬器都是用來幹那個的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_25e9635c:


    c "對..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_e2dbd01f:


    c "你有伊娃的數字化身檔案嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_fc8c2111:


    j "伊娃女士..."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_7ae0c1d9:


    j "是的，我有她的檔案。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_47daa08e:


    c "你能把它加載一下，通過接口訪問嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_ee6b18b5:


    j "是的，我能。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_6b40c0a7:


    j "我猜沒人需要知道這事吧？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_5aa79f8f:


    c "沒錯。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_533657e8:


    c "我想和她說說話。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_78763257:


    j "明白了，主人。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_cd26bd5e:


    c "我覺得那樣更好。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_03036399:


    c "我只是想和她說說話...{w}再次見到她。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_94285da7:


    j "我懂。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_61774a2f:


    j "你該明白它不會和現實生活一樣的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_6effa739:


    c "你不用操心那個。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_5132cac7:


    c "是的，我知道，但總比沒有強。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_4af247bd:


    j "我會幫你弄好的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_139c6bba:


    c "好。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_jade_talk_e897fbb0:


    c "謝謝你。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_a49dfb9c:


    av "[p_name_short]."


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_02719456:


    c "嗨，艾文。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_e2667d55:


    c "你覺得瑞爾怎麼樣？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_68a821a0:


    av "他可不是老媽打過交道的最瘋癲的人。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_b3630d46:


    av "但排名相當靠前。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_e588978b:


    c "他顯得挺多疑的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_bc602c65:


    av "是啊，確實。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_892ab7da:


    av "我猜是工作性質決定的吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_518bb256:


    av "他專攻遺傳學，但對祕密研究項目有種病態的癡迷。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_03b0384a:


    av "有時候人們就是不想讓你插手他們的事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_512578e5:


    c "那堆機器人能保護他嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_0396f3f9:


    av "不好說，不過能讓他安心的話也行。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_7d83b56c:


    av "等我們在森厄星着陸後，老媽會留在船上。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_58a9df96:


    av "等我們在森厄星着陸後，娜迪亞會留在船上。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_ca960896:


    c "她不跟我們一起去？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_a9e2d842:


    av "我讓她別去的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_6dc95381:


    av "我們倆搭檔做這些事很多次了，我知道該怎麼做。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_b2e626d7:


    c "那就只有你和我咯？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_ed2f89e9:


    av "莉莉也想一起來。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_7df34f95:


    c "莉莉？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_77274c31:


    av "對。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_5dd30e94:


    av "我跟她講了我的工作經歷，估計讓她來勁了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_c57132f7:


    av "怎麼，你有意見嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_e7fa47d2:


    c "是的，我擔心她會拖慢我們。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_5a3f3eff:


    av "哇...{w} 呃...{w} 真的？"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_203c7b5e:


    av "你們都經歷過同樣的訓練，[p_name_short]...{w} 我不覺得這裡有什麼問題。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_91336a2a:


    c "不，當然不。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_dd92c143:


    c "只是我沒想到經歷了拉南星上的事後她還會再去野外冒險。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_2252c040:


    av "啊，對了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_df21c389:


    av "我現在要去睡一會兒，如果你不介意的話。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_aven_talk_d7ae8504:


    c "一點不介意。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_celine_talk_e913b734:


    c "哦，抱歉，希望我沒打擾。"


translate traditional_chinese ep003_celine_talk_e6faba8b:


